            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Mike Chen</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Founder, EcoGear Co.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
            "Our organic traffic increased by 580% and online sales tripled. The ROI from our SEO investment has been incredible."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">
              A
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Dr. Amanda Rodriguez</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">MediCare Plus</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 italic">
            "The increase in qualified leads and new patients has been phenomenal. Our practice has grown significantly thanks to Catalyst."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-secondary-600">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll text-white">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Join Our Success Stories?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-white/90">
          Let's create your success story next. Book a free strategy session and discover how we can drive growth for your business.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-primary-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all transform hover:scale-105">
